.. activecode:: er2000
    :author: Eric Reed
    :difficulty: 2.0
    :basecourse: fopp
    :chapter: TransformingSequences
    :subchapter: Exercises
    :topics: TransformingSequences/Exercises
    :from_source: F


    Write a program that will accept words from a user,
    one at a time, until the user types the word 'quit'.
    Start with an empty list, and append each new word to
    that list.  After the user types quit, print out the list
    of words.
    ~~~~